data.description: This 3 story Hunt Club townhome has been beautifully maintained and is ready for it's next owner. Located in Collegeville, Upper Providence Township, Montgomery County and the very desirable Spring-Ford School District.  The lower level has a foyer, family room with sliders to the backyard, and a built in garage.  The main level offers a spacious living room, powder room, kitchen, and dining room with sliders to a 2nd level deck.  The upper level has a primary bedroom with full bath, 2 additional bedrooms, a full hall bath, and a laundry area.  Large backyard open space.  BONUS: HVAC system was replaced in 2013, windows were replaced in 2015, primary bath remodeled in 2015, and the roof was replaced in 2020.  Close to parks, schools, and shopping/dining in Collegeville, Phoenixville, Oaks, King of Prussia.  Plus conveniently located near commuter routes Egypt Rd, Ridge Pk, Rt 363, Rt 422, Rt 29 and the PA turnpike interchange at Valley Forge.  Schedule your appointment to see this home now!
